Title: Turtle Undefeated
Plot: Lux volunteers to host a classmate's party at Baze's loft, hoping to become more accepted by the students at her new school. Cate sees that Lux and Baze have made a great connection and she worries that she will never have a similar relationship with Lux.
ParentalRatingReason: Lightbox Provisional Classification. Official NZ Rating To Be Confirmed.
